    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-11-29T10:06:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-11-29T10:06:00-05:00" n="850"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d850">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Day</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Flay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date ana="#date_imprecise-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" when="1898-11-29T15:15:00+00:09">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 29, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 31.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>Spanish Commissioners at to-day’s conference presented a definite and final
                    acceptance of our last proposition. Next meeting on Wednesday, at which time we
                    will present articles on other matters. They expressed a desire to reach a
                    conclusion promptly. We hope to make good progress from this time.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-11-29T15:15:00+00:09">Monday
                            afternoon, 3.15</date>.</dateline>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Day.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
